DBClusterParameterGroupName.description:
The name of the DB cluster parameter group.

Constraints:

  • Must match the name of an existing DBClusterParameterGroup.

This value is stored as a lowercase string.

DBParameterGroupFamily.description: The DB cluster parameter group family name.

Description.description: The description for the DB cluster parameter group.

Tags.description: The tags to be assigned to the DB cluster parameter group.

items.description: Metadata assigned to an Amazon DocumentDB resource consisting of a key-value pair.

Key.description: The required name of the tag. The string value can be from 1 to 128 Unicode characters in length and can't be prefixed with "aws:" or "rds:". The string can contain only the set of Unicode letters, digits, white space, '_', '.', '/', '=', '+', '-' (Java regex: "^([\\p{L}\\p{Z}\\p{N}_.:/=+\\-]*)$").

Value.description: The optional value of the tag. The string value can be from 1 to 256 Unicode characters in length and can't be prefixed with "aws:" or "rds:". The string can contain only the set of Unicode letters, digits, white space, '_', '.', '/', '=', '+', '-' (Java regex: "^([\\p{L}\\p{Z}\\p{N}_.:/=+\\-]*)$").
